DESCRIPTION

This module tries to predict if and when an ovulation has occurred within the female menstrual cycle
based on basal body temperature values. Taking the temperature values after the ovulation into account
it is possible to predict if an impregnation has occured. This data is often used as the basis for 
basal temperature curves.

WARNING: THE INFORMATION DRAWN FROM THE CALCULATIONS THAT THIS MODULE PROVIDES SHOULD NOT BE USED
AS A MEANS OF CONTRACEPTION!


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following in the distribution
directory:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

